PersonalMission.Name: SPG-9: Collateral Damage
PersonalMission.Description: Powerful HE-shells can not only reduce the hit points of enemy vehicles, but also have a high chance of destroying modules or injuring crew members with splash damage.

Primary.Conditions: Destroy internal modules or injure crew members, totaling at least 3 modules or crew members
